<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:08:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>查克·舒默代表美国犹太人说话吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-20/ty-article/.highlight/does-chuck-schumer-speak-for-american-jews/0000018e-5ca0-d3c4-a7cf-7df4f43d0000</link><description>在发表具有里程碑意义的以色列演讲后，参议院多数党领袖试图平息对犹太建制组织最重要的保护伞团体的担忧。其领导层对他的言论表示持续震惊，而几个成员团体也表达了对舒默的支持</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:41:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-20/ty-article/.highlight/does-chuck-schumer-speak-for-american-jews/0000018e-5ca0-d3c4-a7cf-7df4f43d0000</guid></item><item><title>第 166 天你需要知道的是：内塔尼亚胡表示，准备拉法行动需要时间</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-166-hamas-claims-israel-rejected-cease-fire-proposal/0000018e-5cc0-d411-a3df-dcda44420001</link><description>就在总理内塔尼亚胡准备通过视频向参议院共和党人发表讲话的几个小时前，共和党官员表示，他们正在讨论邀请他在国会联席会议上发言 ■ 哈马斯高级官员表示，以色列对该组织停火提案的反应是否定的 ■ 准备出发内塔尼亚胡表示，在拉法的行动“需要一些时间” ■ 战争结束 166 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:28:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-166-hamas-claims-israel-rejected-cease-fire-proposal/0000018e-5cc0-d411-a3df-dcda44420001</guid></item><item><title>拜登政府在周日截止日期前暂停向以色列出售武器问题上存在分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-administration-split-on-suspending-arms-sales-to-israel-ahead-of-deadline-on-sunday/0000018e-5bea-d949-afae-5beeac6b0000</link><description>以色列远远没有兑现向加沙“大量提供援助”的承诺，使来自美国的武器流动陷入危险</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 16:04:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-administration-split-on-suspending-arms-sales-to-israel-ahead-of-deadline-on-sunday/0000018e-5bea-d949-afae-5beeac6b0000</guid></item><item><title>众议院共和党人考虑邀请内塔尼亚胡在国会联席会议上发表讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/house-republicans-mull-inviting-netanyahu-to-address-joint-session-of-congress/0000018e-5c55-df0b-a78f-ddffb9970000</link><description>这一邀请让人想起内塔尼亚胡2015年的讲话，该讲话旨在争取支持，反对奥巴马政府背后组织的伊朗核协议。此举发生之际，内塔尼亚胡对拜登政府批评以色列在加沙的行为感到明显愤怒</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 15:07:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/house-republicans-mull-inviting-netanyahu-to-address-joint-session-of-congress/0000018e-5c55-df0b-a78f-ddffb9970000</guid></item><item><title>死在以色列监狱的巴勒斯坦人的尸检显示医疗疏忽和瘀伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/autopsies-of-palestinians-who-died-in-israeli-prisons-indicate-medical-neglect-bruising/0000018e-56c6-dea2-a38e-57dfa5430000</link><description>上个月，以色列监狱服务设施中一名行政拘留者和一名安全囚犯死亡，据报道，监狱条件不断恶化，缺乏适当的医疗服务，部分原因是加沙战争爆发以来监狱严重过度拥挤。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:53:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/autopsies-of-palestinians-who-died-in-israeli-prisons-indicate-medical-neglect-bruising/0000018e-56c6-dea2-a38e-57dfa5430000</guid></item><item><title>针对以色列迪莫纳核电站的网络攻击：匿名组织黑客系统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/cyberattack-against-israeli-nuclear-plant-in-dimona-anonymous-group-hacks-system/0000018e-5bc2-d4f6-a9be-dbeab3d60000</link><description>匿名组织在社交媒体上发帖称，其黑客已成功窃取了迪莫纳核反应堆的文件，并删除了他们入侵的计算机系统上的一些信息。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:27:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/cyberattack-against-israeli-nuclear-plant-in-dimona-anonymous-group-hacks-system/0000018e-5bc2-d4f6-a9be-dbeab3d60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长收回取消以色列奖的决定，颁奖典礼将按计划举行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/israels-education-minister-backtracks-on-israel-prize-cancellation-awards-to-be-held/0000018e-5bf4-d9a8-a5ae-fffdcfe50000</link><description>约夫·基什 (Yoav Kisch) 部长否认在得知科技巨头和民主活动人士埃亚尔·瓦尔德曼 (Eyal Waldman) 获奖后取消了今年的奖项，但表示希望避免“不必要的争论”</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:26:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/israels-education-minister-backtracks-on-israel-prize-cancellation-awards-to-be-held/0000018e-5bf4-d9a8-a5ae-fffdcfe50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府发言人埃隆·利维因评论加沙援助而被停职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-government-spokesman-eylon-levy-suspended-after-comments-about-gaza-aid/0000018e-5b83-d9a8-a5ae-ffcff3ef0000</link><description>利维被停职之前，英国外交大臣戴维·卡梅伦在推特上回应称，“食品、水、药品或避难设备进入加沙没有任何限制，事实上，过境点的容量已经过剩”</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 11:55:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-government-spokesman-eylon-levy-suspended-after-comments-about-gaza-aid/0000018e-5b83-d9a8-a5ae-ffcff3ef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列不再考虑自由民主；全球指数引用司法政变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-no-longer-considered-liberal-democracy-global-index-cites-judicial-coup/0000018e-5b1e-d191-ad8e-dbde880e0000</link><description>V-Dem 指数指出，以色列现在被认为是“选举民主国家”，但政府对司法系统的攻击和免受酷刑的自由度“大幅下降”——举行选举，但公民自由和法律面前人人平等没有得到保障</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 10:10:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-no-longer-considered-liberal-democracy-global-index-cites-judicial-coup/0000018e-5b1e-d191-ad8e-dbde880e0000</guid></item><item><title>由于援助遥不可及，加沙儿童的营养不良状况不断蔓延</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-aid-waiting-beyond-their-reach-malnutrition-among-gazas-children-keeps-spreading/0000018e-56c7-daff-a9ce-feef835a0000</link><description>海上援助走廊备受关注，但加沙组织表示，陆路供应对于满足紧急人道主义需求至关重要。联合国记录了 16 起援助车队枪击事件，组织认为大部分事件都是以色列军队幕后黑手</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 08:15:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-aid-waiting-beyond-their-reach-malnutrition-among-gazas-children-keeps-spreading/0000018e-56c7-daff-a9ce-feef835a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的利库德集团无法解开萨尔之谜，但他们无论如何都希望他回来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-likud-cant-unravel-the-saar-riddle-but-they-want-him-back-anyway/0000018e-5916-d88e-a39e-7db71ed60000</link><description>吉迪恩·萨尔坚持加入的战时内阁的紧张局势已达到沸点，与本尼·甘茨的冲突似乎迫在眉睫。一位利库德集团部长在谈到这位前以色列国防军司令时表示，“他太亲美了，他已经成为一个烦恼”</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 04:01:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-likud-cant-unravel-the-saar-riddle-but-they-want-him-back-anyway/0000018e-5916-d88e-a39e-7db71ed60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将向参议院共和党发表讲话；布林肯在访问以色列之前抵达沙特阿拉伯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article-live/gaza-officials-at-least-15-killed-in-airstrike-u-s-deeply-worried-over-famine-report/0000018e-59ae-d5db-abdf-59fee1930000</link><description>哈马斯称以色列对其停火提议的反应是否定的 ■ 以色列军方称，在加沙的 Al-Shifa 医院逮捕了 350 名嫌疑人 ■ 两名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸空袭中丧生 ■ 布林肯在以色列访问前抵达沙特阿拉伯</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 02:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article-live/gaza-officials-at-least-15-killed-in-airstrike-u-s-deeply-worried-over-famine-report/0000018e-59ae-d5db-abdf-59fee1930000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡考虑创造性解决方案，将萨尔带入战时内阁，同时将本格维尔排除在外</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-mulls-creative-solution-to-bring-saar-into-war-cabinet-keep-ben-gvir-out/0000018e-5900-d4f6-a9be-d92aa9470000</link><description>总理计划给予吉迪恩·萨尔在战时内阁中的观察员地位，并正在考虑让他成为“定期受邀者”，但极右翼国家安全部长本·格维尔表示，他将要求与萨尔同等的地位</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 23:35:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-mulls-creative-solution-to-bring-saar-into-war-cabinet-keep-ben-gvir-out/0000018e-5900-d4f6-a9be-d92aa9470000</guid></item><item><title>AG 坚称，以色列允许警察使用间谍软件的新法律必须涵盖腐败案件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-law-allowing-police-to-use-spyware-must-cover-corruption-cases-ag-insists/0000018e-58ef-d5db-abdf-58ff8b740000</link><description>司法部长告诉 Itamar Ben-Gvir，她不能支持批准仅适用于涉嫌严重犯罪案件的间谍软件监视的法律</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 23:15:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-law-allowing-police-to-use-spyware-must-cover-corruption-cases-ag-insists/0000018e-58ef-d5db-abdf-58ff8b740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长谴责加拿大外长停止向以色列运送武器的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/report-canada-will-stop-sending-arms-to-israel-foreign-minister-says/0000018e-58a9-d88e-a39e-7dbb83210000</link><description>以色列外交部长表示：“历史将对加拿大当前的行为做出严厉的评价。”加拿大的声明突显了对以色列在加沙行动的批评越来越多，因为西方国家发现自己因向以色列出售武器而陷入困境</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 21:42:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/report-canada-will-stop-sending-arms-to-israel-foreign-minister-says/0000018e-58a9-d88e-a39e-7dbb83210000</guid></item><item><title>两名辛贝特特工在约旦河西岸枪击事件中受伤；巴勒斯坦人在另一起事件中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/two-shin-bet-agents-wounded-in-west-bank-attack-palestinian-killed-in-separate-incident/0000018e-581e-d7fb-a1df-d8fe78930000</link><description>来自杰宁的 30 岁袭击者向辛贝特特工开枪，被枪杀；消息人士称，在另一起事件中，一名 43 岁的巴勒斯坦人被犹太定居者枪杀。这一说法遭到以色列国防军消息人士的驳斥，他说该男子在袭击以色列国防军士兵后被杀死。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 20:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/two-shin-bet-agents-wounded-in-west-bank-attack-palestinian-killed-in-separate-incident/0000018e-581e-d7fb-a1df-d8fe78930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列确实存在哈斯巴拉问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-19/ty-article/.highlight/israel-really-does-have-a-hasbara-problem/0000018e-57e4-d9a8-a5ae-ffed63bf0000</link><description>如果在国际上还有人愿意为以色列挺身而出，他能说一口流利的英语，牢牢掌握美国的自由主义价值观，并且能够满足内塔尼亚胡严格的纯洁性测试——请他们站起来吗？在内塔尼亚胡发号施令时可能不会</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 18:54:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-19/ty-article/.highlight/israel-really-does-have-a-hasbara-problem/0000018e-57e4-d9a8-a5ae-ffed63bf0000</guid></item><item><title>贾里德·库什纳称加沙海滨财产“非常有价值”，建议以色列“将人们转移出去然后清理”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/jared-kushner-gaza-seaside-land-very-valuable-israel-must-move-people-out-clean-up/0000018e-57b3-d4f6-a9be-dfbb4ed30000</link><description>在接受哈佛大学采访时，特朗普的白宫高级顾问将潜在的巴勒斯坦国描述为“一个超级糟糕的主意”，并建议以色列“在内盖夫推土机”来安置流离失所的巴勒斯坦人，以便重建加沙并“完成工作”</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 18:11:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/jared-kushner-gaza-seaside-land-very-valuable-israel-must-move-people-out-clean-up/0000018e-57b3-d4f6-a9be-dfbb4ed30000</guid></item><item><title>你需要知道的，第 165 天：卡塔尔称拉法行动可能危及停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-165/0000018e-57c9-d9a8-a5ae-ffcd316f0000</link><description>拜登表示，他告诉内塔尼亚胡派团队前往华盛顿，讨论如何在不针对拉法行动的情况下针对哈马斯美国因涉嫌战争罪暂停向以色列转让武器 ■ 白宫对最近一份称加沙迫在眉睫的饥荒的报告“深表关切” ■ 战争结束 165 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 17:49:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-165/0000018e-57c9-d9a8-a5ae-ffcd316f0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔在与以色列摩萨德主席会谈后表示，拉法入侵可能导致加沙人质协议谈判破裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/rafah-invasion-risks-breakdown-of-negotiations-qatar-says-after-talks-with-mossad-chief/0000018e-5773-d5fc-adde-77ffbe3d0000</link><description>以色列代表团目前正在多哈参加另一轮人质交易和停火协议谈判，但以色列当局、人质家属和美国之间仍对协议条件和当前行动存在争议</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 17:24:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-19/ty-article/.premium/rafah-invasion-risks-breakdown-of-negotiations-qatar-says-after-talks-with-mossad-chief/0000018e-5773-d5fc-adde-77ffbe3d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>